label.phrase: this is another swedish heritage spot now considered a ghost town if you like getting a bit off the beaten path and seeing things as they used to be this would be a great choice it's easy to reach on u s route 190 in the beautiful texas hill country the town remains show what happened when the railroad by-passed the settlement almost 100 years ago
